    "name": {
      "zh": "M249 SAW 5.56x45 轻机枪",
      "en": "M249 SAW 5.56x45 light machine gun"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "M249",
      "en": "M249"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "M249 SAW（班用自动武器）是一款采用气吹式自动机和气冷枪管的轻机枪，被美军广泛列装。该枪于1984年列装部队，旨在解决班组层面持续自动火力不足的问题。M249 SAW兼具机枪的射速与突击步枪的精度及便携性。",
      "en": "The M249 SAW (Squad Automatic Weapon) is a gas operated and air cooled light machinegun widely used by the U.S. Armed Forces. The weapon was introduced in 1984 to address a lack of sustained automatic fire capability at the squad level. The M249 SAW combines the rate of fire of a machine gun with the accuracy and portability of an assault rifle."
    },
